CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778875556
OL,3,CPeston: Will Starmer announce a
OL,4,Cdeparture timetable sooner than people
OL,5,Cthink?
OL,7,FTo be clear, any PM that says he's off
OL,8,Fis weakened by that very pledge. But
OL,9,FStarmer might actually have even less
OL,10,Fauthority in today's limbo, where
OL,11,Feveryone but he acknowledges the
OL,12,Freality that he is a short-dated stock.
